  "title": "Radiographer",
  "description": "<p><strong>Lifescan Imaging is looking for experienced Radiographers to join the dynamic team:</strong></p><p>The radiographer will be responsible for performing at least two of the following imaging procedures, and the duties assigned will depend on his/her professional training:</p><ul><li><p>Ultrasound</p></li><li><p>Computer Tomography</p></li><li><p>Magnetic Resonance Imaging</p></li><li><p>Mammography</p></li><li><p>X-Ray</p></li><li><p>BMD</p></li></ul><p><strong>Requirements</strong></p><ul><li><p>Diploma/ Degree in Radiography from a recognized institution with at least 5 years of experience</p></li><li><p>Must possess required AHPC Certification</p></li><li><p>Mature and possess a strong sense of commitment and dedication</p></li><li><p>Able to work in a team or independently with minimum supervision</p></li><li><p>Able to present a professional image and deliver top-quality customer service</p></li></ul>",
