    "description": "<p>Incorporated in 2005, Singapore Medical Group (SMG) is a private specialist and primary healthcare provider with a network of more than 25 medical specialties. Spearheaded by CEO Dr Beng Teck Liang and Healthcare veteran Mr Tony Tan, SMG embarked on a rapid expansion since 2013. The Group is committed to its promise of providing patient centred medical care and experience to every individual.</p>\n\n<p>SMG has more than 30 clinics strategically located in Paragon, Mount Elizabeth Novena Specialist Centre, Parkway East Medical Centre, Raffles Place, Connexion and Gleneagles Medical Centre with a growing network of SMG Associates clinics all across the island.</p>\n\n<p>SMG operates a 24-Hour patient assistance centre hotline service that serves Singapore and international patients.</p>\n\n<p>SMG is listed on the Singapore Exchange (SGX) since 2009.</p>\n\n<p>SMG Clinics: Astra Laparoscopic & Robotic Centre for Women and Fertility, Astra Women’s Specialists Centre, Cardiac Centre International, SMG Kids Clinic, Lifescan Imaging, Lifescan Medical Centre, LSC Eye Clinic, SMG Orthopaedic Group, SMG Specialist Centre, SMG Urology Centre with Beng Surgery,  SW1 Clinic, The Cancer Centre, The Dental Studio, The Obstetrics & Gynaecology Centre, Wellness & Gynaecology Centre by Dr Julinda Lee</p>\n",
